{"tid":877233,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"【蘇加訪港】或帶克羅地亞來港友賽","createTime":"2018-10-26T07:47:12.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-28T18:48:31.000Z","uid":34572,"like":21,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":19,"replies":[{"pid":"53ae19fe262e2d9f018a60c1474f7ff47512dc93","tid":877233,"uid":34572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:47:12.000Z","msg":"足總今日舉行會員午餐會，除邀請各會員及傳媒，還有前世界盃金靴獎得主、現任克羅地亞足總會長的蘇加(Davor Suker)亦有出席，並與香港足總簽署合作伙伴備忘錄。<br />\n<br />\n蘇加在席上分享近年克羅地亞足球發展，並強調草根足球的重要性。雖然與香港足總還未有確實的合作計劃，但他表示願意開放各個層面的技術交流。<br />\n<br />\n問到蘇加會否帶領應屆世界盃亞軍克羅地亞來港友賽時，他就說十分喜歡香港，只要球隊不與歐洲的賽事相撞，來年或者就能夠成事。<br />\n<br />\n#克羅地亞 #蘇加<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地啲臨時克羅地亞人終於可以再蒲頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7ce577d60974875f4c32912e386b2a11c9ed44b0","tid":877233,"uid":134997,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T07:49:02.000Z","msg":"我三十年克羅地亞粉絲+世一球王摸的頭號粉絲"},{"pid":"962f3a110172d3b8c0ce7f1732bad4b8e1c58df2","tid":877233,"uid":52006,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:16:05.000Z","msg":"會唔會請埋冰島?<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"19c81b9fd062c4f5fa8d9e94164a810a6aa48b57","tid":877233,"uid":5649,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:16:39.000Z","msg":"樓主又jer <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2205108467c314fab10585ef652977a1016c180e","tid":877233,"uid":27785,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:18:24.000Z","msg":"客套說話姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"af275102721f8b05a762a3de165d6db15068481f","tid":877233,"uid":59283,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T08:19:35.000Z","msg":"挫敗巴<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},